> 对应地，在 Java 中即可抽象为如下节点结构：
> ```java title:"字典树"
> class TrieNode {  
> 	TrieNode[] child = new TrieNode[26];  
> 	boolean isEnd;  
> }  
> ```
> 其中：
> - `child[i]`：表示当前节点指向的下一个字符节点，下标 `0 ~ 25` 分别对应字符 `'a' ~ 'z'`
> - `isEnd`：用于标记当前节点是否为某个单词的结尾

```java title:"题解"
class Trie {  
    TrieNode root;  
  
    public Trie() {  
        root = new TrieNode();  
    }  
  
    public void insert(String word) {  
        TrieNode node = root;  
        for (char c : word.toCharArray()) {  
            int index = c - 'a';  
            if (node.child[index] == null) {  
                node.child[index] = new TrieNode();  
            }  
  
            node = node.child[index];  
        }  
        node.isEnd = true;  
    }  
  
    public boolean search(String word) {  
        TrieNode node = root;  
        for (char c : word.toCharArray()) {  
            int index = c - 'a';  
            if (node.child[index] == null) {  
                return false;  
            }  
            node = node.child[index];  
        }  
        return node.isEnd;  
    }  
  
    public boolean startsWith(String prefix) {  
        TrieNode node = root;  
  
        for (char c : prefix.toCharArray()) {  
            int index = c - 'a';  
            if (node.child[index] == null) {  
                return false;  
            }  
            node = node.child[index];  
        }  
        return true;  
    }  
  
    class TrieNode {  
        TrieNode[] child = new TrieNode[26];  
        boolean isEnd;  
    }  
}
